'''海港–加州大學洛杉磯分校醫學中心'''（{{lang-en|Harbor–UCLA Medical Center}}），位於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯縣|洛杉磯縣]][[托倫斯|托倫斯]]<ref name="ladhs">{{cite web|url=http://www.harbor-ucla.org/about/contact-us/|title=Contact Us|work=Harbor–UCLA Medical Center|publisher=[[Los_Angeles_County_Department_of_Health_Services|Los Angeles County Department of Health Services]]|access-date=2018-05-18|quote=1000 West Carson Street, Torrance, California 90509|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118221702/https://www.harbor-ucla.org/about/contact-us/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1946年建立<ref>{{citation |newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=February 20, 1946 |title=County Moves for Purchase of Army Hospital |page=14}}</ref>，是[[加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校|加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校]]的教學醫院<ref>{{citation |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=November 11, 1962 |title=Harbor General to Shed Barracks |page=CS 1}}</ref>，亦是洛杉磯縣{{le|南灣區（洛杉磯縣）|South Bay (Los Angeles County)|南灣區}}的{{le|創傷中心|Trauma center|1級創傷中心}}。

